cutscene_segment_set(0, "Leaping from the comic pages in the palm of your hand to the treacherous cliffs of Ludicrous World, it's the X-Freaks!", spr_cutscene_xfreaks_1,,, msc_cutscene_normal);
cutscene_segment_set(1, "Les Slaypool: 'Finally, a good multiverse story! Not to mention a Primus joke I've somehow never seen anyone make. Is Mr. Freaksdev a genius or what? (psst, if we kiss his ass as hard as possible maybe we'll get a spinoff!)'");
cutscene_segment_set(2, "Gloverine: 'Will you quit yappin' for five seconds and let the guys with brains get some words in?'");
cutscene_segment_set(3, "Les Slaypool: 'Hey now, you're as big a spotlight hogger as I am! But yeah, aight, I'll let Sir Patrick Stewart here take the mic for a hot minute.'");
cutscene_segment_set(4, "Professor T: 'Thank you. As my fourth wall demolishing friend here has made all too clear, we are the X-Freaks of Universe SF-1963X. We fight for all freaks, mutants, and freak mutants, and all three are in grave danger!'");
cutscene_segment_set(5, "Cyquops: 'There's been a lot of multiversal chaos rippling through our neck of the woods thanks to Sticky, The Shadow, and Calliginis, but your Kranion is such an idiot, he could very well make things even worse.");
cutscene_segment_set(6, "Gloverine: 'So we're offerin' ya his head served to ya, diced up with my claws! Hell, maybe ya can take our Kragneto instead if ya really need a big lug causin' trouble. At least he ain't as bad a guy!'");
cutscene_segment_set(7, "Tikiman: 'They seem like upstanding gentlemen. I say we let them help us.'");
cutscene_segment_set(8, "Gambi: 'Well yeah, the next level is Barrel Canyon, and we've been sick of exploding barrels for 20 years now.'");
cutscene_segment_set(9, "Les Slaypool: 'It's go time!! OK scoutmaster, say the thing!");
cutscene_segment_set(10, "Cyquops: 'To me, my X-Freaks!'", spr_cutscene_xfreaks_5,,,,, cutscene_transitions.NA);
cutscene_segment_set(11, "...", spr_cutscene_xfreaks_2,,,,, cutscene_transitions.NA);
cutscene_segment_set(12, "", spr_cutscene_xfreaks_6,,,, sfx_bonk_coconut_1, cutscene_transitions.shake);
cutscene_segment_set(13, "Les Slaypool: 'Well that happened.'");